Improve Journey Performance with Recommendations

During journey validation, Journey Builder proactively surfaces configuration recommendations that can elevate performance. Get recommendations regarding stale content, long timeouts for custom activities, long waits at the end of a journey, and transactional journeys.

Where: This change applies to Marketing Cloud Engagement in Corporate and Enterprise editions and to customers with the Journey Builder add-on.
